<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 13:01:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>B-21袭击者首次拍摄空中加油照片</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/b-21-raider-photographed-aerial-refueling-for-the-first-time</link><description>&lt;p&gt;据称，随着美国空军在 2027 年投入使用之前加速生产，B-21 的测试进展很快。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/b-21-raider-photographed-aerial-refueling-for-the-first-time"&gt;B-21 袭击者首次拍摄到空中加油的&lt;/a&gt;照片首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 05:17:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/b-21-raider-photographed-aerial-refueling-for-the-first-time</guid></item><item><title>史诗般的愤怒第11天：美国承诺对伊朗进行“最猛烈的打击”</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/epic-fury-day-11-u-s-promises-most-intense-day-of-strikes-on-iran</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着伊朗无人机和导弹继续飞行，美国增加了部署在英国的轰炸机部队。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/epic-fury-day-11-u-s-promises-most-intense-day-of-strikes-on-iran"&gt;史诗般的愤怒第 11 天：美国承诺对伊朗进行“最猛烈的打击”&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 23:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/epic-fury-day-11-u-s-promises-most-intense-day-of-strikes-on-iran</guid></item><item><title>塞尔维亚MiG-29似乎配备了中国超音速防区外导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/serbian-mig-29-fighter-appears-armed-with-chinese-supersonic-standoff-missiles</link><description>&lt;p&gt;中国制造的 CM-400 空对地导弹以前只在巴基斯坦服役，现在已经出现在塞尔维亚 MiG-29 喷气式飞机上。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/serbian-mig-29-fighter-appears-armed-with-chinese-supersonic-standoff-missiles"&gt;塞尔维亚 MiG-29 似乎配备了中国超音速防区外导弹&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 22:51:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/serbian-mig-29-fighter-appears-armed-with-chinese-supersonic-standoff-missiles</guid></item><item><title>发现前往波斯湾的伊朗无人机的能力取得巨大飞跃</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/massive-leap-in-ability-to-spot-iranian-drones-headed-to-persian-gulf</link><description>&lt;p&gt;E-7A 楔尾飞机可以说是世界上发现低空飞行的伊朗无人机和巡航导弹的最佳飞机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/massive-leap-in-ability-to-spot-iranian-drones-headed-to-persian-gulf"&gt;发现前往波斯湾的伊朗无人机能力的巨大飞跃&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 22:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/massive-leap-in-ability-to-spot-iranian-drones-headed-to-persian-gulf</guid></item><item><title>美国用弹道导弹袭击伊朗海军舰艇</title><link>https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-striking-iranian-navy-ships-with-ballistic-missiles</link><description>&lt;p&gt;使用弹道导弹远距离打击敌方舰艇是美军未来发展的预演。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-striking-iranian-navy-ships-with-ballistic-missiles"&gt;美国用弹道导弹袭击伊朗海军舰艇的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 16:19:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/land/u-s-striking-iranian-navy-ships-with-ballistic-missiles</guid></item><item><title>突击队突袭确保伊朗浓缩铀可能成为非常危险的必需品</title><link>https://www.twz.com/nuclear/special-operations-raid-to-secure-irans-enriched-uranium-may-become-a-very-risky-necessity</link><description>&lt;p&gt;突袭充满风险，但它可能成为确保核材料安全且不落入该政权手中的唯一途径。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/nuclear/special-operations-raid-to-secure-irans-enriched-uranium-may-become-a-very-risky-necessity"&gt;突击队突袭以确保伊朗的浓缩铀可能成为一种非常危险的必需品&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 21:58:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/nuclear/special-operations-raid-to-secure-irans-enriched-uranium-may-become-a-very-risky-necessity</guid></item><item><title>随着对伊朗的空袭继续进行，B-52 轰炸机抵达英国基地（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/b-52s-arrive-at-u-k-base-as-air-campaign-over-iran-grinds-on</link><description>&lt;p&gt;其中三架战略轰炸机加入了部署在英国皇家空军费尔福德的美国空军远程打击资产队伍，队伍不断壮大。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/b-52s-arrive-at-u-k-base-as-air-campaign-over-iran-grinds-on"&gt;随着对伊朗的空袭继续进行，B-52 战机抵达英国基地（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;中。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 21:56:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/b-52s-arrive-at-u-k-base-as-air-campaign-over-iran-grinds-on</guid></item><item><title>贝尔的 X-76 折叠旋翼飞机是 DARPA 最新的 X 飞机</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/bells-x-76-fold-away-rotor-aircraft-is-darpas-newest-x-plane</link><description>&lt;p&gt;X-76 计划于 2028 年首飞，将探索带折叠旋翼、载人和无人的快速飞行、不依赖跑道的飞机技术。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/bells-x-76-fold-away-rotor-aircraft-is-darpas-newest-x-plane"&gt;贝尔的 X-76 折叠旋翼飞机是 DARPA 最新的 X 型飞机&lt;/a&gt;这篇文章首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Mar 2026 21:33:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/bells-x-76-fold-away-rotor-aircraft-is-darpas-newest-x-plane</guid></item><item><title>伊朗对珍贵导弹防御雷达的攻击敲响了警钟</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iranian-attacks-on-critical-missile-defense-radars-are-a-wake-up-call</link><description>&lt;p&gt;伊朗成功瞄准中东关键导弹防御雷达，凸显了全球的脆弱性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iranian-attacks-on-critical-missile-defense-radars-are-a-wake-up-call"&gt;伊朗对珍贵导弹防御雷达的攻击是一个警钟，&lt;/a&gt;该文章首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 22:31:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iranian-attacks-on-critical-missile-defense-radars-are-a-wake-up-call</guid></item><item><title>针对伊朗的空战进入第二周（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/air-war-against-iran-enters-week-two</link><description>&lt;p&gt;由于霍尔木兹海峡的航运几乎陷入停滞，伊朗继续瞄准其邻国的石油生产。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/air-war-against-iran-enters-week-two"&gt;针对伊朗的空战进入第二周（已更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Mar 2026 21:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/air-war-against-iran-enters-week-two</guid></item></channel></rss>